SUMMARY:Hamilton Saturday Salsa
DESCRIPTION:Language Exchange Toronto - Se Habla English & Spanish\n🔥 **SalsaSoul Saturdays is heating up the winter season in Hamilton!**\n\nEvery third Saturday of the month\, the Main Stage at 747 King Street E transforms into a vibrant hub of salsa and bachata\, welcoming dancers of all levels for unforgettable nights of rhythm\, community\, and pure fun.\n\nGuests are invited to arrive as doors open at **7:30 p.m.**\, followed by a **Beginner Salsa Lesson at 8:00 p.m.**\, perfect for newcomers or anyone looking to warm up. The energy rises as the **Latin Dance Party kicks off from 9:00 p.m. to 1:00 a.m.**\, featuring a lively mix of primarily salsa and bachata.\n\nAdmission is **$20 for the party** or **$25 including the lesson**\, and each ticket includes a complimentary drink. Advance tickets are also available through the event’s ticket link:\nhttps://www.zeffy.com/en-CA/ticketing/salsa-soul-saturday-jan-17--2026\n\nThe venue offers **free on-site and neighbourhood parking**\, along with a **cash bar** for guests to enjoy throughout the night. No partner or prior dance experience is required—everyone is welcome to join the celebration.\n\nSalsaSoul Saturdays promises fiery music\, warm community vibes\, and a dance floor ready for all who want to move.\n\n**Winter just got a lot hotter.**\n\nMore Information:\nhttps://www.salsasoulproductions.com/\nhttps://www.facebook.com/salsasoulproductions/\n\nSee you there....\nHéctor
